Name: HORIZON 1003333NV Welders Jacket, 2X
Description: Introducing our Long Welders Navy Jacket, meticulously crafted for durability and safety in mind. Constructed from 100% Cotton FR with a sateen finish, weighing 10 OZ (340 gsm), it ensures both comfort and protection during welding tasks. Featuring a brass zipper with aramid tape and a center front flap secured by metal snaps, it offers additional shielding against sparks and heat. The collar is equipped with a hook and loop closure for added protection. Adjustable metal snaps at the wrist allow for a customizable fit. Stay organized with 2 waist pockets, each adorned with flaps for secure storage. Highlighted by brown contrast stitches, this jacket combines functionality with style, making it an essential garment for welders in any environment.

Name: Terra 112900Y2XL Workwear,-  3 In 1 Rainsuit, Polyester , Yellow,2Xl

Name: TERRA 116632OR Rainpant with Removable Straps, Orange
Description: These waterproof and breathable rain pants are crafted from durable 300-denier Oxford polyester with a polyurethane coating, ensuring protection against the elements. The elastic waist and removable elastic sash with a zipper provide a customizable fit, while convenient side openings allow easy access to inner layers. Featuring sealed water-repellent seams, a self-gripping fly with snap, and leg zippers with ankle cuffs, these pants combine functionality and comfort. For added safety, they are equipped with reflective tape, enhancing visibility in low-light conditions.
